            fullStory: 'RRR director S.S. Rajamouli\'s new epic, along with two independent films, received Academy Award nominations in Best International Feature and Best Original Score categories. Indian films grossed $2 billion internationally in 2025, a 40% increase. Streaming platforms are investing heavily in Indian content. The government announced a film tourism incentive to promote shooting locations. Pan-Indian releases are now common, with films dubbed in 8+ languages for global audiences.',
